Class CSVNLinesSequenceRecordReader

  • java.lang.Object

          • org.datavec.api.records.reader.impl.csv.CSVNLinesSequenceRecordReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, Configurable, RecordReader, SequenceRecordReader

    public class CSVNLinesSequenceRecordReader
extends CSVRecordReader
implements SequenceRecordReader
    A CSV Sequence record reader where:
    (a) all time series are in a single file
    (b) each time series is of the same length (specified in constructor)
    (c) no delimiter is used between time series
    For example, with nLinesPerSequence=10, lines 0 to 9 are the first time series, 10 to 19 are the second, and so on.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
